{"data_shared": "When you download, access, and use the App, it may use technology to automatically collect Usage Details, Device Information, Stored Information and Files, and Location Information. The app also collects information about the location of your device to tailor your user experience.",
  "data_collected": "When you download, register with, or use this App, we may ask you to provide Personal Information such as name, age, gender, postal address, email address, or telephone number. Additionally, the app automatically collects information like IP address, user name, usage patterns, and search queries. The App may also collect and use real-time information about your device’s location through the device’s privacy settings.",
  "security_practices": "We will take reasonable steps to protect the information we collect from loss, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, the transmission of information via the internet and mobile platforms is not completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your personal information."}

{"data_shared": "We may share your Information with trusted third parties, service providers, or partners during the course of our business. Any disclosure of your Information will comply with the terms of this Privacy Policy.",
  "data_collected": "We may collect your personally identifiable information, including but not limited to, contact information and information about your use of the Services, including your responses and information about your device or platform on which you access the App (together, your “Information”).",
  "security_practices": "We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational security measures designed to protect the security of any Information we collect from unauthorized access or malicious actions."}

{"data_shared": "Eyewind may use and disclose to Eyewind’s partners and contractors the collected non-personal data for purposes of analyzing usage of the Services, investigate, prevent or take action regarding unauthorized use of the services to further develop the Services and other Eyewind services and products.",
  "data_collected": "The data we collect depends on the context of your interactions with us, the choices you make, including your privacy settings, and the products and features you use. The data we collect can include SDK/API/JS code version, browser, Internet service provider, IP address, platform, timestamp, application identifier, application version, application distribution channel, independent deice identifier, iOS ad identifier (IDFA), Android ad master identifier, network card (MAC) address, and international mobile device identification code (IMEI) The equipment model, the terminal manufacturer, the terminal device operating system version, the session start / stop time, the location of the language, the time zone and the network state (WiFi and so on), the hard disk, the CPU, and the battery use, etc.",
  "security_practices": "Eyewind follows generally accepted industry standards and maintains reasonable safeguards to attempt to ensure the security, integrity and privacy of the information in Eyewind’s possession."}

{"data_shared": "When using our services some information may be processed by third parties: photos may be processed by image processing services, statistical information may be collected by our service providers and technical information may be collected for improving the service.",
  "data_collected": "We collect some raw information which may be considered as personally identifiable, which is technical information about your device, such as your IP address, your operating system and other technical information. Moreover, when you register, we may retain the information you provided us at registration, including your name, photo and email address. If you use one of our server side services, we may also retain a copy of the data submitted to our server for a limited time.",
  "security_practices": "We provide the service on an 'as-is' and 'as-available' basis. Your use of the service is at your own risk and under your liability. We make no warranty that (i) the service will meet your requirements and (ii) the service will be uninterrupted, timely, secure, or error-free and (iii) the results that may be obtained from the use of the service will be accurate or reliable and (iv) the quality of any products, services, information, or other material purchased or obtained by You through the Service will meet your expectations, or (v) any errors in the Service will be corrected."}

{"data_shared": "Images and Videos entered by the user are sent to the app server in order to be retrieved later by the user himself, and so that the app can offer the functionalities according to its description. We allow third-party companies to serve ads and collect certain anonymous information when you visit our app. These companies may use anonymous information such as your Google Advertising ID, your device type and version, browsing activity, location and other technical data relating to your device, in order to provide advertisements.",
  "data_collected": "The app doesn't collect any user personal data as, for example, name, picture or location.",
  "security_practices": "Consequently, the app doesn't share any personal information with any other entity or third parties."}

{"data_shared": "Celsys obtains customers’ personal information only to the extent and scope required for conducting its business. Personal information shall not be disclosed to any third party, excluding cases with express permission from the customer or as required by law. In cases of disclosure to a third party, they are obligated to take measures against information breaches and handle the personal information safely with due diligence.",
  "data_collected": "Celsys collects customers' personal information for various purposes, including the sale, provision, and leasing of products, services related to these, Clip Studio account services, promotions, conducting surveys and monitoring for service development, responding to inquiries, and fulfilling contracts. Personal information includes details like address, name, age, email address, etc. of customers using their services.",
  "security_practices": "Celsys employs security measures such as SSL encryption to protect personal information. They appoint officers responsible for handling personal information, identify employees who handle personal information and establish a reporting system for any violations. Regular employee education on handling personal information is conducted. Access to personal information is restricted, and subcontracted handling of personal information is managed through contracts and supervision."}

{"data_shared": "Samsung shares personal information internally within its corporate family and with business partners, service providers, and other parties as required by law or necessary to protect its services. This includes affiliates within the Samsung Electronics Group, business partners for providing services, carefully selected service providers such as cloud platform services, and others as required by current law or as necessary for legal processes, corporate transactions, or with your consent.",
  "data_collected": "Samsung collects personal information including basic and sensitive personal data as per Vietnamese law for using its services. This includes name, nickname, date of birth, gender, phone number, password, email address, and credit card information. Additionally, they collect contact information, details provided related to personal data and product or service usage, device and service information, hardware information, software versions, identification numbers, diagnostic and usage data, and location information with your consent.",
  "security_practices": "Samsung processes personal data for identifying and authenticating users securely, providing services, improving and customizing user experience, linking accounts with third-party services, responding to requests, providing personalized advertising with consent, operating and improving its services and business operations, preventing fraud and legal liabilities, and complying with legal regulations. Personal data is also used for interacting with promotional programs and for advertising purposes with user consent."}

